revisions.description: Added agent capabilities definitions for MPLS-LSR-STD-MIB.
Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names. Added IP TTL Propagate object to the MPLS scalar group.
Added RowStatus support to the minor layer and the tunnel profile groups.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniMplsAgentV1.name: juniMplsAgentV1
juniMplsAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the MultiProtocol Label Switching (MPLS) component of the
        JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version of the MPLS component was supported in
        JUNOSe 4.0 system releases.
